    "description": "Cat Herders is a chaotic 1-4 player, split-screen coop game. It's about herding cats. Each level has a goal, and your job is to get the troublesome cats into that goal as quickly as possible using a variety of items!<br><br>We just pushed our big Anniversary Update which improves gameplay and the UI a whole bunch!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/c5e15a9261f7fbd620e32701485ca6e8.poster.avif?t=1699324838\" width=450 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/c5e15a9261f7fbd620e32701485ca6e8.webm?t=1699324838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/c5e15a9261f7fbd620e32701485ca6e8.mp4?t=1699324838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/5d179d9e826e98fe327c927601abe1b6.avif?t=1699324838\" width=450 height=74 /></span><br>Use items like tuna, your computer keyboard and Cat Snax™ to draw cats towards the goal. Use scarier items like a barking robot dog to push them in whichever direction you please. Use more chill items like the music box to put them to sleep while you figure out a plan of attack. Use the cat trap to move multiple cats quickly. Create chaos with the cat cannon!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/25684ce7ea64964dd813e7c2b562b720.avif?t=1699324838\" width=450 height=74 /></span><br>Coordinate with your friends in 2-4 player split-screen (Steam Remote Play/Parsec friendly!) to get the cats to the goal as fast as you can. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/34716c741cf2efb2408240e7913735ba.avif?t=1699324838\" width=450 height=74 /></span><br>Compete to finish each level in the fastest time with gold, silver and bronze medal times. Compare your times to other cat herders on the online leaderboards!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183920/extras/9f942c0335a680a529212554f9815a2b.avif?t=1699324838\" width=450 height=74 /></span><br>Halloween and Christmas maps have been added! Herd cats in the abandoned medieval village while being hunted by the spoopy ghost cat or entice cats with presents in a beautiful winter wonderland.<br><br>",
